Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Lang-b%E1%BA%A1t-1/poem---47YegzrbA6Tz7P9nkc1A">Lang bạt 1 - 狼跋1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Xu%C3%A2n-Hi%E1%BB%81n/L%C6%B0u-gi%E1%BA%A3n-thi/poem-QIQ6w2fdK4487KZkN9eDeQ">Lưu giản thi - 留柬詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Xu%C3%A2n-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-BV5Qt58ZUK6yTC9_FIEtmA">Phan Xuân Hiền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%C3%A1i-tr%C3%AC-1/poem-Uow1pylJ67QZwThJ5OUBJg">Tái trì 1 - 載馳 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/T%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-QJK74_J02inWJMEPxc2HOg">Tự thán kỳ 2 - 自歎其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/author-7tg_rhleFYVL5Ann2EB2iA">Trần Danh Án</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3mvgQ8jqLVNdE0oNQACUCg">Vịnh hoài kỳ 2 - 詠懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
